config.script:
# Import the system module to access tag functions
	from system.tag import write
	
	# Define the path to your memory tag
	tag_path = "[default]International/Pollution Gate Visibility"
	
	# Read the current value of the tag
	current_value = system.tag.read(tag_path).value
	
	# Toggle the value of the tag
	new_value = not current_value
	
	# Write the new value back to the tag
	write(tag_path, new_value)

transforms.expression: if ({value}, 'Pollution Gate Visibility Off', 'Pollution Gate Visibility On')
